Account management for workers
  observable on worker profile, modifications are direct to the database
photos/videos management for workers
payment system for workers (pay for a year subscription, monthly...)
workers can refresh(to be in the top of the list) their profile by paying a small fee

certification about worker's photos (ask for a photo with phrase, object, pose and check if the other pictures are similar. might use a neural network if possible. Otherwise, create admin accounts to check the photos)

create admin accounts for collaborators
  check photos/videos
  manage requests from users and workers
  check payments

When the homepage is loaded, the workers' profiles are loaded by priority. When a profile updates his priority, show a small notification to the user if he wants to reload the page.

Advertising
  clients can pay small fee to remove ads (2 chf per month)
  workers can pay small fee to remove ads (2 chf per month)
